	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Mobile</placeName> <date>Febry 7th 1857</date></p>
				<p>My Dear Friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Your letter of the<lb/> <date>30th</date> reached me only today &#38; too<lb/> late for reply by return mail<lb/> &#38; I have been so much engaged<lb/> through the day that this is the<lb/> first moment I could devote<lb/> to you.  As it is 10 P. M. I shall<lb/> write but a few lines &#38; get<lb/> it off if possible by the morning<lb/> mail.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I need not say to you<lb/> how deeply <persName>M</persName> &#38; I were pained<lb/> to hear of your misfortune<lb/> you must be aware that<lb/> we feel it as sensibly as if it<lb/> were our own&#8212;more so in<lb/> fact&#44; as we have never met<lb/> with a serious loss like this<lb/> &#38; could bear it better perhaps<lb/> than you can in your present<lb/> state of health.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I must scold<lb/> you a little now however&#8212;</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>you know that I am at your<lb/> service as far as I have the<lb/> power &#38; yet you give me<lb/> no particulars&#44; or anything to<lb/> form a guess even about your<lb/> obligations or wants&#8212;this is<lb/> not right &#38; you know it.  It<lb/> is not what I would have done<lb/> to you&#44; were our positions reversed<lb/> &#38; therefore as soon as you get<lb/> this sit down &#38; give me the<lb/> figures &#38; let me see if I can<lb/> do anything to assist you.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I shall remit you by <date>Tuesdays</date><lb/> mail &#36;500&#8212;to help you through<lb/> with any immediate payments<lb/> you may have to make&#8212;<add>&#63;</add><lb/> I hope to hear either through<lb/> yourself or <persName>Nell<add>&#63;</add></persName> something more<lb/> of your affairs.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">My eyes are very<lb/> much fatigued tonight &#38; I must<lb/> close this now.  Our nurse very<lb/> foolishly mistook the moonlight last<lb/> night for daylight &#38; woke us all up</p>
			<pb n="2R"/>
				<p>at 3 A. M. since when I have<lb/> not had a wink of sleep &#38; my eyes<lb/> are dim in consequence.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The children &#38; <persName>M</persName> are well<lb/> so am I&#8212;<persName>Dew</persName> the best the<lb/> worst&#44; the most provoking &#38; the<lb/> dearest little creature in the<lb/> world&#8212;E<add>&#63;</add> not to be <add>&#63;</add>d<lb/> anywhere.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Hoping to hear from<lb/> you again shortly &#38; with<lb/> assurances of our deep regret<lb/> at the loss you have sustained<lb/> we remain</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Yr sincere friends</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">M &#38; S Wolff</persName></p>
				<p>I did not get my letter off after<lb/> all &#38; consequently enclose you<lb/> check for &#36;500 this morning.<lb/>  will send you more as soon<lb/> as I know your wants.<lb/>  <sic>Dont</sic> be disheartened at my<lb/> rate.</p>
		</body>
